9 and Lockdown Plan compliant with Section 404 of the North Carolina Fire
10 Code.
11 (4) A family child care home shall have carbon monoxide alarm and detection
12 systems compliant with Section 915 of the North Carolina Building Code.
13 (5) A family child care home shall have smoke alarms compliant with Section
14 R907 of the North Carolina Building Code.
