40 site and provide notice to persons who have requested notice of proposed guidelines. In addition,
41 the State Board must accept oral and written comments on the proposed guidelines during the 15
42 business days beginning on the first day that the State Board has completed these notifications.
43 For the purpose of this subsection, a technical amendment is either of the following:
