20 Program as a competitive grant program for the purpose of increasing the number of
21 professionally licensed teachers in the State and improving teacher competency, student
22 outcomes, and teacher retention in the State. The Department of Public Instruction shall
23 administer the Program in collaboration with ApprenticeshipNC as set forth in this section.
