1 (3) For eleventh grade students not meeting the career and college readiness
2 standards established by the State Board of Community Colleges, a plan for
3 enrolling in remedial coursework for his or her senior year.
4 (4) Any other minimum requirements established by the Superintendent.
5 SECTION 7.45.(h) Reporting Requirement. – The Superintendent or a local board
