44 a. Executive Committee meetings shall be open to the public, except that
45 the Executive Committee may meet in a closed, nonpublic meeting as
46 provided in subdivision (2) of subsection (f) of this section.
47 b. The Executive Committee shall give 30 days' notice of its meetings,
48 posted on its website and as determined to provide notice to persons
49 with an interest in the business of the Commission.
