38 "(70) To Provide Students the Suicide and Crisis Lifeline Phone Number and the
39 NC Peer Warmline Phone Number. – A local board of education shall adopt
40 a policy to ensure all schools in the local school administrative unit provide
41 students the phone numbers for the Suicide and Crisis Lifeline and the NC
42 Peer Warmline. The board shall verify that the phone numbers for the Lifeline
