1 Cambridge Advanced International Certificate of Education (AICE) program
2 who meets the following criteria:
3 a. Is employed by, or retired having last held a position at, one or more
4 of the following:
5 1. A qualifying public school unit.
6 2. The North Carolina Virtual Public School program.
7 b. Taught one or more students who received a score listed in subsection
8 (c) of this section.
9 (2) Eligible career and technical education (CTE) teacher. – A teacher who meets
10 the following criteria:
11 a. Is employed by, or retired having last held a position at, a qualifying
12 public school unit.
