38 year to be allocated to the North Carolina Collaboratory to establish and operate the Office of
39 Learning Research (OLR), beginning in the 2024-2025 fiscal year. The purpose of OLR is to
40 identify and evaluate the efficacy and efficiency of programs, activities, initiatives, procedures,
41 and any other factors related to elementary and secondary education in the State.
