33 CODIFY NORTH CAROLINA PATRIOT STAR FAMILY SCHOLARSHIP PROGRAM
34 SECTION 8A.9.(a) Article 23 of Chapter 116 of the General Statutes is amended by
35 adding the following new Part to read:
36 "Part 9. North Carolina Patriot Star Family Scholarship Program.
37 "§ 116-209.120. Program established.
38 The Board of Governors of The University of North Carolina shall establish the North
39 Carolina Patriot Star Family Scholarship Program. To the extent funds are made available for the
40 Program, the Board shall award funds for the purpose of administering scholarships under the
41 Program to (i) the Patriot Foundation, a nonprofit corporation, and (ii) the Marine Corps
42 Scholarship Foundation, Inc., a nonprofit corporation.
43 "§ 116-209.122. Purpose of the Program.
44 The Patriot Foundation and the Marine Corps Scholarship Foundation, Inc., respectively,
45 shall provide for scholarships to eligible children and eligible spouses of certain veterans, eligible
46 children of certain currently serving members of the Armed Forces, and eligible disabled veterans
47 to attend eligible postsecondary institutions in accordance with the requirements of this Part.
48 "§ 116-209.124. Definitions.
49 For the purposes of this Part, the following definitions shall apply:
