3 DEFINE SEPSIS/NORTH CAROLINA MEDICAID PROGRAM
4 SECTION 9E.21.(a) Except as provided in subsection (b) of this section, the
5 Department of Health and Human Services, Division of Health Benefits (DHB), shall ensure that
6 the Medicaid program (i) complies with the most recently published American College of Chest
7 Physicians/Society of Critical Care Medicine (ACCP/SCCM) sepsis guidelines, primarily known
8 as the Surviving Sepsis Campaign guidelines, and (ii) does not utilize any clinical criteria beyond
9 that described in the ACCP/SCCM sepsis guidelines when making any medical necessity or
10 utilization review determinations related to diagnosis, treatment, and management of sepsis.
11 DHB shall amend all relevant clinical coverage policies and rules, or adopt rules, policies, or
12 guidelines, necessary to implement this section.
