29 Symphony raise at least seven million dollars ($7,000,000) in non-State funds for the 2025-2026
30 fiscal year and seven million dollars ($7,000,000) in non-State funds for the 2026-2027 fiscal
31 year. The North Carolina Symphony cannot use funds transferred from the organization's
32 endowment to its operating budget to achieve the fundraising targets set out in subsections (b)
33 and (c) of this section.
