32 (6) Historic Bath.
33 (7) Historic Edenton.
34 (8) Historic Halifax.
35 (9) North Carolina State Capitol.
36 (10) Reed Gold Mine.
37 (11) Roanoke Island Festival Park.
38 (12) Somerset Place.
39 (13) Thomas Day State Historic Site.
