15 SECTION 40.1.(c) The Department of Information Technology shall use funds
16 appropriated for the Growing Rural Economies with Access to Technology program for fixed
17 wireless and satellite broadband grants, established in G.S. 143B-1373.2 to award grants to
18 eligible entities to purchase installation materials for satellite internet service. Installation
19 materials must be for the grantee's own use and not for distribution to other parties. No portion
20 of funds granted under this section shall be used for internet service subscriptions. The
21 Department shall prioritize grant applicants that will deploy installation materials in one of the
22 39 counties designated as a disaster area due to Hurricane Helene. The Department may also give
23 priority to grantees that offer emergency services, disaster relief, educational services, or
24 economic development.
