34 repairing, or replacing broadband infrastructure, provided that all of the following apply:
35 (1) An applicant for funding under this section shall only be permitted to recovery
36 costs that are not subject to reimbursement from another source of external
37 funding, including insurance.
38 (2) The Department may cap reimbursement at a portion of the costs incurred
39 based upon evaluation of considerations, such as the number of applications
40 anticipated compared to funds available.
41 (3) Priority shall be given to restoration of broadband service.
