43 "§ 116E-2. Purpose of the North Carolina Longitudinal Data System.
44 (a) The North Carolina Longitudinal Data System is a statewide data system that contains
45 individual-level student data and workforce data from all levels of education and the State's
46 workforce. The purpose of the System is to do the following:
