32 Universities, Inc., and nonpublic schools may transfer student data and workforce data to the
33 System in accordance with the data security and safeguarding plan developed under G.S. 116E-5.
34 (c) All data sharing supported by the System shall comply with all applicable federal and
35 State data and data privacy laws and regulations."
