1 "§ 58-86-41. Amount due for membership; payments credited to separate member
2 accounts.
3 (a) Unless otherwise provided under this Article, each member of the Pension Fund shall
4 pay the sum of fifteen dollars ($15.00) per month to the Pension Fund for membership in the
5 fund for a period not to exceed 20 years.
6 (b) Unless otherwise provided under this Article, all payments due in any calendar year
7 shall be made no later than March 31 subsequent to the end of the calendar year in which the
8 payment was due.
